	  <section class="project-description">
	    <h2 class="section-title">Project Overview</h2>
	    <p class="description-text">
	      This is a web application designed to handle user registration and login using <strong>MySQL</strong>, <strong>JavaEE Servlets</strong>, and <strong>JSP</strong>. The system ensures security with features like <strong>cookies</strong> for user sessions and <strong>DataSource</strong> management for database connectivity. 
	    </p>
	    <p class="description-text">
	      The application allows for the creation of <strong>projects</strong>, where users can perform CRUD operations (Create, Read, Update, Delete) to manage projects' data with persistence. It also includes functionality for assigning users to tasks and removing users from those tasks as needed.
	    </p>
	    <p class="description-text">
	      The system is hosted on <strong>Tomcat 10.1</strong> for reliable performance and scalability, providing an efficient development and deployment experience for both small and large applications.
	    </p>
	  </section>
	  
